wiki.summary: "Lifestyle" is the eleventh track on LISA’s solo album, Alter Ego. With heavy bass and rapid beats, “Lifestyle” is an unapologetic anthem that revels in living large, defying expectations, and embracing a world of luxury and freedom. The song was first introduced in an activity LISA and her team created for her fans, allowing them to connect their music to discover which alter ego of hers matches their vibe and get a sneak preview of an unreleased track. This track was revealed when they received her alter ego, Speedi. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: "Lifestyle" is the eleventh track on LISA’s solo album, Alter Ego. With heavy bass and rapid beats, “Lifestyle” is an unapologetic anthem that revels in living large, defying expectations, and embracing a world of luxury and freedom. The song was first introduced in an activity LISA and her team created for her fans, allowing them to connect their music to discover which alter ego of hers matches their vibe and get a sneak preview of an unreleased track. This track was revealed when they received her alter ego, Speedi. As one of the biggest global music icons, LISA is always moving through various realms—music, fashion, and beyond. On “Lifestyle,” she not only embraces her fast-paced life but also boldly flaunts it, owning every moment of her success. Read more on Last.fm.
